ell she used to do the best she could. I'll tell you what they used to do. Used to go to the butcher, you couldn't do it now, and you used to get a shillings}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8598532\charrsid16449734  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
