\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12858205 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11080425\charrsid16449734 What would you do at dinnertime then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4735342 EC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11080425\charrsid16449734 Just have a - a sandwich or something like that, or a - bit of cold meat a
nd pickle, you know, nothing very elaborate because we used to have a - our cooked meal at night time. 'Cos it - she couldn't do both. She couldn't cook a meal dinnertime and then again at night time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12858205 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11080425\charrsid16449734 What did you do on Saturdays then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4735342 EC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11080425\charrsid16449734 Dinnertime Saturdays, 'cos dad was home. And Sunday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12858205 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11080425\charrsid16449734 Didn't he work Saturdays then?
